        "\u00bd cup chicken stock",
        "\u00bc cup balsamic vinegar",
        "\u00bc cup orange juice",
        "1 teaspoon honey",
        "1 tablespoon cornstarch",
        "\u00bc cup chicken stock",
        "1 cup fresh blueberries",
        "2 teaspoons chopped fresh chives",
        "4 (6 ounce) salmon steaks",
        "2 tablespoons olive oil",
        "salt and pepper to taste"
    ],
    "directions": [
        "Pour 1/2 cup chicken stock, vinegar, orange juice, and honey into a saucepan",
        "Bring to a boil over high heat, then reduce heat to medium",
        "Dissolve cornstarch in 1/4 cup of chicken stock, and stir into the simmering sauce",
        "Cook and stir until the sauce thickens and turns clear, 1 to 2 minutes",
        "Stir in the blueberries and chives, and keep warm over low heat",
        "Preheat grill to medium high-heat",
        "Brush salmon with oil, and season to taste with salt and pepper",
        "Grill until the fish flakes easily with a fork, about 3 to 4 minutes per side",
        "Serve with blueberry sauce"
